---
description: Database and migration rules
globs: ["sql/**/*.sql", "backend/app/models/**/*.py", "backend/app/services/**/*.py"]
alwaysApply: true
---

# Database Rules

- MySQL is the system database.
- Distinguish file_instance and file_content.
- Do not use filename as identity.
- Use SHA256 content hash for content identity.
- Schema changes require migration files.
- Do not store large binary files in MySQL.
